This is a hack, and I&#39;m not sure if it works, but you could try having your
servlet run ant directly (assuming you have ant setup to run the JUnit
tests).

Something like:

  String[] args = { &quot;-buildfile&quot;, &quot;pathtofile&quot;, &quot;junit&quot; };
  org.apache.tools.ant.Main.main(args);

Have ant run the tests, format them to HTML pages, then view the results
from your browser.

